### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ========================================
### Trust Analytics Endpoints
### ========================================

### Get Trust Timeline - All Communities
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me/trust/timeline
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Get Trust Timeline - Filter by Community
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me/trust/timeline?communityId=123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Get Trust Timeline - Filter by Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me/trust/timeline?startDate=2024-01-01T00:00:00Z&endDate=2024-12-31T23:59:59Z
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Get Trust Timeline - Filter by Community and Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me/trust/timeline?communityId=123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000&startDate=2024-10-01T00:00:00Z&endDate=2024-10-31T23:59:59Z
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Get Trust Timeline - Invalid Date Range (Should Fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me/trust/timeline?startDate=2024-12-31T23:59:59Z&endDate=2024-01-01T00:00:00Z
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Get Trust Timeline - Invalid UUID (Should Fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me/trust/timeline?communityId=invalid-uuid
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Get Trust Timeline - Invalid Date Format (Should Fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me/trust/timeline?startDate=2024-01-01
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Get Trust Timeline - No Auth (Should Fail with 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me/trust/timeline

###

### ========================================
### Trust Summary Endpoints
### ========================================

### Get Trust Summary - All Communities
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me/trust/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Get Trust Summary - Filter by Community
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me/trust/summary?communityId=123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Get Trust Summary - Invalid UUID (Should Fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me/trust/summary?communityId=invalid-uuid
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Get Trust Summary - No Auth (Should Fail with 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me/trust/summary

###

